data.description: Get set for a fresh beginning in this charming 4-bed, 2.5-bath, 2-story home with around 2,200 sq ft. Tucked in a serene cul-de-sac, it's your tranquil escape in a quiet neighborhood.The front porch is perfect for relaxation and welcomes. Inside, a formal dining room and open kitchen make family gatherings and entertaining a breeze. The cozy living room with a gas fireplace offers warmth and character. The main-level master suite features a double vanity, jacuzzi tub, separate shower, and a roomy walk-in closet. Outside, a covered patio with an outdoor grill area awaits, creating the ideal space to entertain friends and make lasting memories. With top-notch schools nearby, this is your perfect haven for a fulfilling and peaceful life. So, it's time to pack your bags and start a new chapter in this freshly painted, delightful home!
